---
[v1] arm64: dts: mt7988: add pce node

Add PCE (Packet Classification Engine) device node for MT7988. The hardware is
designed to classify certain format packet and forward them to specific NETSYS
port to offload APMCU's burden.

---
v1: Move openwrt-master files to openwrt-25.12 branch after OpenWrt official
    25.12 branch release.
---

--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/mediatek/mt7988a.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/mediatek/mt7988a.dtsi
@@ -329,6 +329,12 @@
 			status = "disabled";
 		};
 
+		pce: pce@15100000 {
+			compatible = "mediatek,pce";
+
+			fe_mem = <&eth>;
+		};
+
 		sgmiisys0: syscon@10060000 {
 			compatible = "mediatek,mt7988-sgmiisys",
 				     "mediatek,mt7988-sgmiisys0",
